cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with object reconstruction from images using deformable 3D models and automatic object segmentations. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper deals with 3D surface reconstruction from 2D images. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper mentions learning deformable 3D models from 2D annotations. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with automated object reconstruction. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with reconstructing objects in realistic scenes from single images.
